$BR
\(d3 = \) \{&ans_rule(30)\}
$BR
\(p3(x) = \) \{&ans_rule(30)\}
$BR
\(q3(x) = \) \{&ans_rule(30)\}
$PAR 
and \(\int\int_Rf(x,y)dA=\int_a^b\int_{g(y)}^{h(y)}f(x,y)dxdy\) where
$BR
\(a = \) \{&ans_rule(30)\}
$BR
